                    κ</supplied>άρφη ἥμε<supplied reason="lost">ρα : <gap reason="lost" atLeast="1" atMost="3" unit="character"/> : ἄ<lb n="7" break="no"/>γρια</supplied> : <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character" precision="high"/></lem>
